-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/19.mp3","time_start":64.54,"time_end":65.84},{"position":20,"content":"...and that's Peacetown, you said?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/20.mp3","time_start":65.84,"time_end":69.16},{"position":21,"content":"So how did you hear about our club?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/21.mp3","time_start":69.37,"time_end":72.11},{"position":22,"content":"Did you look on the internet?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/22.mp3","time_start":72.11,"time_end":74.09},{"position":23,"content":"I usually do that, but this time...","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/23.mp3","time_start":74.09,"time_end":77.34},{"position":24,"content":"well, I was talking to a relative the other day and he suggested it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/24.mp3","time_start":77.34,"time_end":82.56},{"position":25,"content":"Oh, is he a member too?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/25.mp3","time_start":82.56,"time_end":84.84},{"position":26,"content":"He belongs to another club,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/26.mp3","time_start":84.84,"time_end":86.95},{"position":27,"content":"but he'd heard good things about yours.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/27.mp3","time_start":86.95,"time_end":89.73},{"position":28,"content":"OK.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-