d/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/46.mp3","time_start":138.31,"time_end":141.66},{"position":47,"content":"Not yet, but I have entered three in the past.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/47.mp3","time_start":141.66,"time_end":146.17},{"position":48,"content":"Oh, that's interesting.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/48.mp3","time_start":146.17,"time_end":148.09},{"position":49,"content":"So why don't you tell me something about those?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/49.mp3","time_start":148.09,"time_end":151.35},{"position":50,"content":"Let's start with the first one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/50.mp3","time_start":151.35,"time_end":153.47},{"position":51,"content":"Well, the theme was entitled 'Domestic Life'.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/51.mp3","time_start":153.64,"time_end":158.02},{"position":52,"content":"I see.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/52.mp3","time_start":158.02,"time_end":159.23},{"position":53,"content":"So it had to be something related to the home?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/53.mp3","time_start":159.23,"time_end":162.43},{"position":54,"content":"Yeah.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-18-test-3-part-1-2023-06-17-11-12-53/54.mp3","time_start":162.43,"time_end":163.15},{"position":55,"content":"I chose to take a photo of a family sitting round the dinner table having a mea